ciscoSwitchCefMIB.name: ciscoSwitchCefMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoSwitchCefMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-lan-switch-snmp@cisco.com
ciscoSwitchCefMIB.description: This MIB module defines management objects for the CEF features on Cisco Layer 2 and Layer 3 devices. Definition of some of the terms used in this MIB: CEF - Cisco Express Forwarding. VPN - Virtual private network. VRF - VPN Routing and Forwarding instance. MPLS - Multiprotocol Label Switching EoMPLS - Ethernet over MPLS

cscSwitchCefStatsTable.name: cscSwitchCefStatsTable
cscSwitchCefStatsTable.description: This table provides CEF statistics for switching engines.

cscSwitchCefStatsEntry.name: cscSwitchCefStatsEntry
cscSwitchCefStatsEntry.description: An entry providing CEF statistics information maintained by a particular switching engine entity (identified by entPhysicalIndex). An entry of this table is created if a switch engine with these CEF statistics is detected by the managed system. An entry of this table is deleted if the removal of the switching engine itself.
